{"tid":1827101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族！我嘅同胞！我哋一齊撐住，直至香港達到最終勝利，OK？","createTime":"2020-01-16T16:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T03:24:59.000Z","uid":131691,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3936e4b6d713a98e8739f05c208a72b0ec2c9052","tid":1827101,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:28:12.000Z","msg":"對唔住，又飲大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好想香港人記得，其實有唔少（所謂精英嘅）人係想香港人達到最終勝利㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUeo5vO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUeo5vO.jpg&h=deca0461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你知唔知有幾多（所謂精英嘅）人其實係推動緊革命！<br />\n我好慚愧，點解同一team嘅人，有人被捕，要流放，我反而走得甩，破解到圍捕冇被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪我膽小，走得快過朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭必須要面對斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習近平必須要面對斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路！</span>"},{"pid":"321c5218cc059474965b43268e1f3e9b68b4802d","tid":1827101,"uid":36088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a220bd18d6770ebd5d1a174ecea042fc7cbb05","tid":1827101,"uid":224052,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"Sorry 細佬才疏學淺，嗰兩個襟章代表啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919dc2a046d8bf4f2be4dbcc10682a603def87f9","tid":1827101,"uid":35301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabee9735c6b206a534a5ec792a9fa9eb16bb309","tid":1827101,